## Keyboards
  ### Shortcut to change keyboard layout
  You need to execute the following at startup / login. To do that, add the following in /etc/profile. If you using zsh, make sure /etc/zsh/sprofile enables compatibility mode.
  ```setxkbmap "fr,us" -option grp:alt_shift_toggle```
